Universal Pictures has revealed a teaser of upcoming movie &#8220;The Mummy.&#8221;The 15-second clip doesn&#8217;t give much away but does promise that a full trailer is to come on Sunday, December 4.Directed by Alex Kurtzman, the film stars Tom Cruise, Russell Crowe and Sofia Boutella and is set to be released in theaters June 9, 2017.-Relaxnews